MBOMBELA –  An escaped convict who was on the run, has been nabbed this morning. According to Phoenix Security Jurie Grobler, Difference Mathebula was wanted by police for apparently escaping from custody a few months back.  “Our security was at the bus stop when they saw the pamphlet from the police with his photograph on it.” Read more here: Local Gangsters among four dead He said as they were patrolling the bus area they spotted Mathebula in the crowd. ” They apprehended him and contacted the police who came to fetch him.” 